import bisect

def fibonacci_square_sum(n):
    fibonacci = [0, 1]
    squares = [0, 1]
    total = 2
    for _ in range(2, n):
        next_fibonacci = fibonacci[-1] + fibonacci[-2]
        fibonacci.append(next_fibonacci)
        square = next_fibonacci ** 2
        total += square
        bisect.insort(squares, square)
    return (squares, total)
